This is README for Jamendo HTML5 Player

This player is pure HTML and Javascript. Idea is to make an HTML5 app.
Main page is written with PHP, but only to render it more easilly. You can "compile" the page by running:
 php mobile.php > index.html

Directories:
js - keeps all the javascript

3rd party libraries:
jQuery
jQuery Mobile
jPlayer

3rd party libraries should be fetched from corresponding CDN locations.
